name: Murky's - Penis on Cheek LoRA
description:
Do you want to support me? Consider being a patron on Patreon to vote on train polls and access stuff early. ❤️

Trained with 150 images.

This LoRA enhances "Penis on Cheek" concept where cheek is pressed with penis.

List of prompts you might need are

penis, solo focus, cheek poking, hetero, penis on face, poking, one eye closed, penis awe,erection, cheek squash, large penis, cheek press

90% of the time it will create 2 penis. You can try to change weight or mix with some negatives "multiple penises, 2boys" if you prefer only 1. Also you can combine with facial expressions to get some funny results

Use weight around 0.8 and 1 depending on model and your prompts

I'm trying some new training settings lately so not uploading rapidly as I used to. Sorry ^^'
